window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All I want is to pay the rent and find a boyfriend. But an insane vampire thinks I hold the key to his takeover of the city, and I have a new stalker.</p> <p>At least for now, I've dodged the Illuminati's Hunters, but life is still a little too challenging. Rival vampire lords want to use me against each other, and the mysterious members of the Columbia Club are offering bounties for vampires and werewolves.</p> <p>I'm lucky that the gang at Rosie's has my back, because I'm going to need them.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
